            "title": "即月期指開跌304點     低水305點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指開報24,906，跌304點或1.21%，低水305點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科指期貨開報4,629，跌71點或1.51%，低水69點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國指期貨開報8,259，跌91點或1.09%，低水94點。</p>\n</div>",
